spell_list.description: The dirge's impairments that affect encounters will siphon a portion of what they impair back to the dirge's group. Mitigation impairments will grant the group a triggered effect instead of mitigation.
spell_list.description_pvp: The dirge's impairments that affect encounters will siphon a portion of what they impair back to the dirge's group. Mitigation impairments will grant the group a triggered effect instead of mitigation.

effect_list.description: Zander's Choral Rebuff will grant a triggered damage effect that applies on spell attacks.
Clara's Chaotic Cacophony will grant a triggered damage effect on melee attacks.
Daro's Sorrowful Dirge will increase the group's attack speed and movement speed.
Disheartening Descant will increase the group's strength and agility.
